an>就拿我来说，<span class="_ _3"></span>父亲早已去</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y69 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">世，<span class="_ _5"></span>母亲现在都<span class="_ _19"> </span>80 岁了，<span class="_ _16"></span>但还是每天牵挂着我。<span class="_ _5"></span>前段时间，</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y6a ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">我去了香港<span class="_ _19"> </span>7 天，<span class="_ _16"></span>母亲天天给我打不通电话，<span class="_ _16"></span>就特别特别挂</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y6b ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">念。<span class="_ _9"></span><span class="lse">我想天下父母对儿女都是如此，<span class="_ _9"></span><span class="ls25">哪怕自己到了垂暮之年，</span></span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y6c ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">也念念不忘自己的子女，一直惦记着。 </div><div class="t m0 x22 h4 y8c ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">但遗憾的是，如今很多子女，有了各方面的能力以后，</div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
